data.description: Updated, remodeled, flipped, and dressed up ready for the show. This 2 bed, 1.5 bath ranch home with an attached 2 car garage has had some exciting updates. The kitchen layout has been transformed and given newly painted cabinets, new counters, sink, faucet, and an island with a wood top. Plus new LVP flooring. The spacious living room has been given new carpet. The master bedroom has doubled in size (formally 2 bedrooms) and now boosts a "his and hers" closet and new carpet. Plus there are newly painted walls and trim throughout. The enclosed patio received a new overhead door so it can be used as an indoor/outdoor patio space, or as a garden shed. Lastly, there is a new exterior door. This home is ready to show off for you, come take a look.,Short sale is being professionally processed by Universal Short Sales,LLC. Buyer Responsible Short Sale Processing Fee of 10,000.00. Please review "Presentation of Offers" document before submitting offer. Property sold AS-IS
